# SPA has no client-side routing — it always lives at `/`.
# We intentionally do NOT add a catch-all `/*  /index.html  200` here:
# otherwise Cloudflare Pages would silently serve index.html as the body
# of missing `/assets/*.js` requests (stale Telegram cache → SyntaxError →
# blank screen). With no redirect rules, Pages returns a real 404 for
# missing assets, the <script> onerror fires, and the inline boot-fallback
# in index.html shows a helpful "clear Telegram cache" message.
